#: ../../source/network/http/webdav.rst:2
msgid "WebDAV"
msgstr "WebDAV"

#: ../../source/network/http/webdav.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/http/webdav.rst:6
msgid ""
"WebDAV （Web-based Distributed Authoring and Versioning） 一种基于 HTTP "
"1.1协议的通信协议。它扩展了HTTP 1.1，在GET、POST、HEAD等几个HTTP标准方法以外添加了一些新的方法，使应用程序可对Web "
"Server直接读写，并支持写文件锁定、解锁，以及版本控制等功能。"
msgstr ""
"WebDAV (Web-based Distributed Authoring and Versioning) is a communication "
"protocol based on HTTP 1.1. It extends HTTP 1.1 by adding new methods "
"beyond standard HTTP methods such as GET, POST, and HEAD. These methods "
"allow applications to read from and write to a web server directly, and "
"support file write locking, unlocking, version control, and related "
"features."

